I can name a ton of people that I know a lot about, but really don't know their exact whereabouts.  Hell, my own brother, who just left me a message, is somewhere in New York.  I could tell you pretty much his entire life story, but I couldn't direct a taxi to pick him up where he currently stands. . . <br>
